{"questionId":"9514","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\frac{{4x - 5}}{{{x^2} - 3x + 2}}\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>5</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x \\ne 1{\\text{,}}\\,x \\ne 2\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Use part (a) to find the exact value of&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\int\\limits_{ - 1}^0 {f(x)dx} \">\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi>f</mi>\n    <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;giving the answer in the form&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{ln}}\\,q\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>q</mi>\n</math></span>,&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"q \\in \\mathbb{Q}\">\n  <mi>q</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">Q</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\int\\limits_{ - 1}^0 {\\frac{1}{{x - 1}} + \\frac{3}{{x - 2}}{\\text{ }}} dx = \\left[ {{\\text{ln}}\\left| {x - 1} \\right| + 3\\,{\\text{ln}}\\left| {x - 2} \\right|} \\right]_{ - 1}^0\">\n  <munderover>\n    <mo>∫</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n  </munderover>\n  <mrow>\n    <mfrac>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mn>1</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </mfrac>\n    <mo>+</mo>\n    <mfrac>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>x</mi>\n        <mo>−</mo>\n        <mn>2</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtext>&nbsp;</mtext>\n    </mrow>\n  </mrow>\n  <mi>d</mi>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <msubsup>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>[</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>ln</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mn>3</mn>\n        <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n        <mrow>\n          <mtext>ln</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <mi>x</mi>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mo>|</mo>\n        </mrow>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>]</mo>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>0</mn>\n  </msubsup>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = \\left( {3\\,{\\text{ln}}\\,2} \\right) - \\left( {\\,{\\text{ln}}\\,2 + 3\\,{\\text{ln}}\\,3} \\right) = 2\\,{\\text{ln}}\\,2 - 3\\,{\\text{ln}}\\,3 = \\,{\\text{ln}}\\frac{4}{{27}}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>ln</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>ln</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>ln</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>ln</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>4</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>27</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9514","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.3c","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Use part (a) to find the exact value of ∫ − 1 0 f ( x ) d x , giving the answer in the form ln q , q ∈ Q .","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.11—Partial fractions"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}